<p class="clear">
	About last night:
	<br />
	My first Argentine milonga was at Club Gricel. Our unwieldy, large tour group (thirty-five people or so) went right when the club opened. When we left at 2AM or so the place still wasn't as legendarily crowded as I'd heard Buenos Aires milongas are. 
</p>
